l6(c<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:644;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2022-09-17 13:22:49";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2022-09-17 11:22:49";s:12:"post_content";s:7200:"[et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" background_color="#ffecd1" custom_padding="||0px||false|false" da_disable_devices="off|off|off" global_colors_info="{}" da_is_popup="off" da_exit_intent="off" da_has_close="on" da_alt_close="off" da_dark_close="off" da_not_modal="on" da_is_singular="off" da_with_loader="off" da_has_shadow="on"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" custom_padding="0px||||false|false" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" header_font="Montserrat|700|||||||" header_text_align="left" header_text_color="#15616d" global_colors_info="{}"]<h1 style="text-align: left;">About</h1>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" text_font="Lato||||||||" text_text_color="#15616d" text_font_size="16px" global_colors_info="{}"]<p style="text-align: left;">Analog is an webshop registered for selling video games, consoles, and gaming equipment. We have been operating since 2021 and represent brands such as PlayStation, Xbox, Electronic Arts, Playground games, Ubisoft...</p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" text_font="Lato||||||||" text_text_color="#15616d" text_font_size="16px" global_colors_info="{}"]<p style="text-align: left;">We offer clients the opportunity to purchase the most famous gaming consoles and deliver the products in the shortest possible time. Our offer also includes the most famous game titles for PlayStation and Xbox. We try to inform our loyal customers about the news from the field of gaming daily and carefully monitor the most important events related to the work of manufacturers, publishers, consoles, games, and accessories.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" custom_padding="||||false|false" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" header_2_font="Montserrat|700|||||||" global_colors_info="{}"]<h2 style="text-align: left;">Services</h2>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure="1_4,1_4,1_4,1_4" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" custom_padding="0px||0px||false|false" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="1_4" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_icon font_icon="&#x7d;||divi||400" icon_color="#15616d" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"][/et_pb_icon][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" text_font="Lato||||||||" text_text_color="#15616d" text_font_size="16px" text_orientation="center" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"]<p><span>All orders are processed between 10.00am to 5.00pm, excluding weekends and holidays.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_4" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_icon font_icon="&#xf48b;||fa||900" icon_color="#15616d" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"][/et_pb_icon][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" text_text_color="#15616d" text_font_size="16px" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"]<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Depending on existing stock availability in the outlet, collection may take a few working days. Please order before Friday for same/next day pickup.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_4" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_icon font_icon="&#xf187;||fa||900" icon_color="#15616d" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"][/et_pb_icon][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" text_font="Lato||||||||" text_text_color="#15616d" text_font_size="16px" text_orientation="center" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"]<p><span>Delivery to your door-step may take up to 5 working days approximately.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_4" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_icon font_icon="&#xf590;||fa||900" icon_color="#15616d" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"][/et_pb_icon][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" text_text_color="#15616d" text_font_size="16px" text_orientation="center" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"]<p>Our technical support is available every day <span>between 10.00am to 5.00pm</span> excluding weekends and holidays.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure="1_3,1_3,1_3" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" custom_margin="||||false|false" custom_padding="||||false|false" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="1_3" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_testimonial author="John" portrait_url="https://nnedeljkovic.wppsbootcamp.com/projekat/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/t1.jpg" portrait_width="100px" portrait_height="100px" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" body_text_align="center" body_text_color="#15616d" body_font_size="16px" text_orientation="center" global_colors_info="{}"]<p>Whenever you need a new game or accessory for PlayStation 5 you can always find it on this webshop. I am delighted with the offer and the speed of delivery.</p>[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_testimonial author="Kylie" portrait_url="https://nnedeljkovic.wppsbootcamp.com/projekat/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/t3.png" portrait_width="100px" portrait_height="100px" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" body_text_align="center" body_text_color="#15616d" body_font_size="16px" text_orientation="center" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"]<p>My brother is a big fan of games and consoles. I didn't know what to buy him as a birthday present but IÂ  found this shop. He was thrilled when he opened the box and saw the new Xbox Series X.</p>[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_testimonial author="Alejandro" portrait_url="https://nnedeljkovic.wppsbootcamp.com/projekat/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/t2.png" portrait_width="100px" portrait_height="100px" _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" body_text_align="center" body_text_color="#15616d" body_font_size="16px" text_orientation="center" locked="off" global_colors_info="{}"]<p>My girlfriend and I love arcade games, especially Mortal Kombat and Call of Duty. I didn't think so much about the anniversary gift. Now we enjoy thanks to PlayStation Digital Editon, and have some fun every night.</p>[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]";s:10:"post_title";s:5:"About";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:5:"about";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2022-09-18 16:00:50";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2022-09-18 14:00:50";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:59:"https://nnedeljkovic.wppsbootcamp.com/projekat/?page_id=644";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"commen